Package edu.cofc.grader

Class SingleTestAbstractMethod

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cofc.grader.Test
      • edu.cofc.grader.SingleTestAbstractMethod
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    SingleTest

    public abstract class SingleTestAbstractMethod
extends Test
    SingleTestAbstractMethod provides an interface for creating a SingleTest
    The test name and result are printed within the run method, so a SingleTest just needs to specify the logic of the test to run and the points for the test in an exec() method.
